snippet.title: Summit Accommodators, Inc. BK - Stephanie Studebaker-DeYoung Deposition - BK Website and Crystal Cox
snippet.description:
August 25, 2009 - Stephanie Studebaker-DeYoung responds to questions asked by attorney David S. Aman about her website summit1031bkjustice.com. Studebaker-DeYoung also responds to questions about Crystal Cox and explains about early personal attacks made by Cox on the Internet.

Studebaker-DeYoung claims she told Cox to read contents published at summit1031bkjustice.com before making gross assumptions and then make her own decisions.

Copyright 2009 United States Bankruptcy Court
